commentText: Checks name and aliases of the given bean for URLs, starting with "/".
codeText: @Override_	protected String[] determineUrlsForHandler(String beanName) {_		List<String> urls = new ArrayList<String>()__		if (beanName.startsWith("/")) {_			urls.add(beanName)__		}_		String[] aliases = getApplicationContext().getAliases(beanName)__		for (String alias : aliases) {_			if (alias.startsWith("/")) {_				urls.add(alias)__			}_		}_		return StringUtils.toStringArray(urls)__	}
